title: Monaco call off team walk ahead of Champions League clash with Manchester City… because it’s raining!
text:
RAIN CHECK Monaco call off team walk ahead of Champions League clash with Manchester City… because it’s raining! 
The wet conditions in Manchester are already getting the better of the Ligue 1 side as AS Monaco bosses opt to keep their pampered stars indoors. Exclusive
